CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

December 12, 2007

[Cite as 12/12/2007 Case Announcements, 2007-Ohio-6518.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2007-1781. State ex rel. Nash v. Court of Appeals, Eighth Appellate Dist.

In Mandamus. On respondents’ motion to dismiss and relator’s motion to strike the motion to dismiss. Motion to strike denied. Motion to dismiss granted. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
